==Russian==
[[Category:Russian nouns]]
===Noun===
'''волкулак''' (volkulák) {{m}}, ''pl'' '''[[волкулаки]]''' (volkuláki)

also can be spelled as [[волкодлак]], [[вовкулак]], [[вовкулака]]

# [[werewolf]] 

===Etymology===
From [[волк]] (''[[wolf]]'') and '''кудло''' (obsolete for ''[[hair]]'') or '''длак''' ([[Slavonic]] for ''hair''). Or, supposedly, from [[Greek]] [[βρυκόλακας]]. Similar Slavonic words: [[vukodlak]] ([[Serbian]]),  [[vlkodlak]] ([[Czech]]), [[wilkołak]] ([[Polish]])

